# ğŸš— Car Sales Dashboard

## ğŸ“Œ Overview
This **Car Sales Dashboard** is an **interactive visualization** created in **Tableau** to analyze **car sales performance** over different **dealers, regions, body styles, colors, and transmission types**. The dashboard provides key **insights** such as **Year-to-Date (YTD) sales**, **weekly trends**, and **company-wise performance**.

The dataset contains **car sales transaction records**, including details like **dealer name, company, model, engine type, transmission, price, and dealer region**.

---

