## ğŸ“‚ Dataset Information
The dataset contains the following fields:
| Column Name        | Description                                     |
|--------------------|-------------------------------------------------|
| `Annual Income`    | Income range of customers purchasing cars      |
| `Dealer_Name`      | Name of the dealership                         |
| `Company`         | Car brand/manufacturer                          |
| `Model`           | Car model name                                  |
| `Engine`          | Engine type (e.g., Overhead Camshaft)           |
| `Transmission`    | Type of transmission (Manual/Auto)              |
| `Color`           | Car color                                       |
| `Price ($)`       | Sale price of the car                          |
| `Dealer_No`       | Dealerâ€™s unique identifier                     |
| `Body Style`      | Type of car (SUV, Sedan, Hatchback, etc.)       |
| `Phone`           | Dealer contact number                          |
| `Dealer_Region`   | Location of the dealership                     |

